In recent months, the U.S. has been suffering record-high inflation – the highest in the past 31 years – which has affected almost every economic sector, with prices for food and other daily necessities skyrocketing. Coupled with a tight supply chain due to the pandemic, American people may have rough days during this holiday season. Credits: Editor: Yuan Xin Designer: Wang Shiqi Senior producer: Wei Wei Managing director: Mei Yan (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)